      "author": "huysgt (HarryNg)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey everyone <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/waving_hand.png?v=15\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>If your team is using tools like DocuSign to collect signatures, you probably know the pain:<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Switching between tools<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Uploading files back to <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Tracking who signed (and who didn’t) manually</p>\n<p>We felt the same pain, so we built an app that lets you send, sign, and track documents directly from your boards.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"video-placeholder-container\">\n  </div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/c/8cda95f65b146342c336344a678d19a9440a1ad4.jpeg\" title=\"upload-signature-modal\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/c/8cda95f65b146342c336344a678d19a9440a1ad4_2_690x347.jpeg\" alt=\"upload-signature-modal\" width=\"690\" height=\"347\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">upload-signature-modal</span><span class=\"informations\">1000×503 31.1 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/9/893c0ccf92c273e635309a364c88270d1f94ef7a.jpeg\" title=\"signing-form-signature-step\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/9/893c0ccf92c273e635309a364c88270d1f94ef7a_2_690x474.jpeg\" alt=\"signing-form-signature-step\" width=\"690\" height=\"474\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">signing-form-signature-step</span><span class=\"informations\">1910×1314 77.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>We’re now opening our <strong>Private Beta</strong> to a small group of <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> users who want a faster, simpler signing experience.</p>\n<p><strong>Beta perks:</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/gem_stone.png?v=15\" title=\":gem_stone:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":gem_stone:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Free access during beta<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=15\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Direct chat with our product team<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/trophy.png?v=15\" title=\":trophy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":trophy:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Lifetime discount for active feedback contributors</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/love_letter.png?v=15\" title=\":love_letter:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":love_letter:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> If you’d like early access, just <strong>drop a comment below or DM me</strong>, and we’ll send you an invite right away.</p>\n<p>You can also <strong>sign up directly here</strong> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> [<a href=\"https://forms.gle/fy9X9ubAakJzJyZUA\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Beta Signup Link</a>]</p>\n<p>We’d love your feedback to help us shape the easiest eSignature experience for <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> teams</p>"
    },
